Assemble the pieces

~~~
'epub unix:chdir
'.. unix:chdir
~~~

zip -0Xq /tmp/book.epub mimetype
zip -Xr9Dq /tmp/book.epub *

Cleanup is the final step. Remove the temporary epub directory

~~~
'rm_-rf_epub unix:system
~~~

